OL,3,CFormer teacher who posed as teen on
OL,4,CSnapchat admits 29 child sex offences
OL,6,FA former teacher who posed as a
OL,7,Fteenager on Snapchat has pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to 29 sex offences against 26
OL,9,Fchildren, including one as young as 10.
OL,11,FSimon Clark, of no fixed abode in
OL,12,FEllesmere Port, Cheshire, worked at a
OL,13,Fschool in north Wales and was arrested
OL,14,Fin August 2023 after police in north
OL,15,FWales were contacted by a concerned
OL,16,Fparent who reported that their teenage
OL,17,Fdaughter had been receiving messages
OL,18,Ffrom an unknown man requesting naked
OL,19,Fimages.
