OL,6,FA warrant was conducted at his home in
OL,7,FMay 2023 and a number of devices were
OL,8,Fseized from the address, with Cheshire
OL,9,FPolice officers later finding that
OL,10,FClark had been posing as a teenager
OL,11,Fusing a Snapchat account.
OL,13,FAppearing at Chester Crown Court on
OL,14,FFriday, 28 March, the 46-year-old
OL,15,Fstared straight ahead as he admitted
OL,16,Fthe offences.
OL,18,FThe charges all relate to 26 victims
OL,19,Funder the age of 16 and took place
OL,20,Fover a seven-year period.
