OL,6,FThey include three counts of inciting
OL,7,Fa child under 13 to engage in sexual
OL,8,Factivity, 21 counts of engaging in
OL,9,Fsexual communication with a child
OL,10,Funder 16, three counts of making
OL,11,Findecent photographs of children, and
OL,12,Ftwo further counts of inciting a child
OL,13,Fto engage in sexual activity.
OL,15,FThe court heard he made 26 indecent
OL,16,Fimages which were classified as
OL,17,FCategory A, along with 29 of Category
OL,18,FB and 81 of Category C.
