OL,6,FClark was released on conditional bail
OL,7,Ffor pre-sentencing reports, while the
OL,8,Fcourt heard he had previously been a
OL,9,Fman of good character.
OL,11,FSitting at Chester Crown Court,
OL,12,FRecorder Eric Lamb told the defendant
OL,13,Fas he stood in the dock: "You have
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to a considerable
OL,15,Fnumber of serious offences against
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,F"Before passing sentencing the court
OL,19,Frequires further information. I shall
OL,20,Fadjourn for six weeks. You will
OL,21,Fcontinue on bail on existing terms."
